{"tid":1758374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【渣打Bonnie Tong懷疑放料畀差佬】整合版 + 懶人包","createTime":"2019-11-27T04:26:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T01:22:43.000Z","uid":202464,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"460032e8929f552a22cf134c266de16fd6d6a568","tid":1758374,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T04:26:21.000Z","msg":"涉事銀行：渣打銀行<br />\n<br />\n涉事員工：青衣城分行經理Bonnie Tong 唐曉華<br />\n<br />\n涉事地點：奥海城分行<br />\n<br />\n涉事日期：2019年8月28日、2019年9月5日<br />\n<br />\n事發經過：<br />\n<br />\n1. Bonnie Tong係上述日期、上述渣打分行，曾4次不當使用其他渣打員工login 銀行系統， check 客戶資料。<br />\n<br />\n（用其他員工login / 密碼，除非事先得到渣打准許，否則係不誠實使用電腦。要渣打交待）<br />\n<br />\n2.  CCTV影到，Bonnie Tong用手機懷疑拍攝電腦畫面<br />\n<br />\n（係咪得到渣打事先准許？否則係盜竊公司機密。）<br />\n<br />\n3. 將客戶資料，直接交比做東九龍反黑組警察老公<br />\n<br />\n（渣打要解釋點解容許員工將客戶資料轉交第三者。）<br />\n<br />\n4. 渣打聲稱交由獨立人士調查，揾左2個退休分行經理調查。其中一人係長沙灣分行時認識Bonnie Tong。<br />\n<br />\n（要渣打解釋點解搵個認識嫌疑人既人士負責調查。促請渣打香港高層親身重新調查）<br />\n<br />\n5. 最少有一名住係黄大仙女手足因被Bonnie 用渣打電腦系統起底，被佢老公拘捕，該女手足只得渣打銀行户口。<br />\n<br />\n（要渣打解釋點樣保障所有客戶私隱）<br />\n<br />\n6. Bonnie Tong 四圍同同事講佢上司Jo Tai幫佢,好快可以番工,自己唔會有事.<br />\n<br />\n（請渣打解釋 Jo Tai係洩密事件中負責咩角色。）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，有無英文好既連登仔幫下手，將上面既野寫成英文？等大家幫手send去英國總部、同相關監管機構？"},{"pid":"cef7d198f628e314cee15ea83c3c663f53b3e24f","tid":1758374,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T04:28:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1784b24e0104f9d832a6ab2196fde7a9e53400aa","tid":1758374,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T04:30:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3950001248d8bf911aa48857bc65800efcb0b976","tid":1758374,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T04:33:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74dc434008457a9eb61749e70e3ebfff06fa36f7","tid":1758374,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T04:33:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08e9dcaeb1e18d14383e9beb11ef6466063cd8a2","tid":1758374,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T04:34:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb5e18986f84cfb5efce31ddc46237cac55d9013","tid":1758374,"uid":274801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T04:34:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d038bf1c809f2b2275ab2d996b0d4f87cab6a07","tid":1758374,"uid":60105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T04:34:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d19352d397656a22c891c980577699a6d3b7a928","tid":1758374,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T04:35:06.000Z","msg":"有無連登仔補充下。有咩係無提到既？"},{"pid":"3165450f3508114f57e0d884ec366a1bbcf5602b","tid":1758374,"uid":297560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T04:35:41.000Z","msg":"這。在我面前走過"},{"pid":"f34e78ddf15466482cc8491879ba30e41fe3bcfa","tid":1758374,"uid":274801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T04:36:07.000Z","msg":"Twitter 都可以"},{"pid":"63ce40d088205921f956d95f16377080b139e4ed","tid":1758374,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f34e78ddf15466482cc8491879ba30e41fe3bc